	"system": {
		"description": "<p>At 14th level, the caustic biles and corrosive fluids that flow through you offer protection against external digestive juices and hazards. You gain immunity to acid damage while in your @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-class-features.Item.Zy5SjEocWsJaxdiy]{Blood Frenzy}.</p><p>Additionally, you can cast the spell @UUID[Compendium.a5e.a5e-spells.Item.lc2gxaul1pp1582i]{Caustic Muck} at 3rd-level without using any components. Intelligence is your casting modifier for this spell. You can upcast this spell by spending 1 hit die as if it were equal to 1 spell slot; for example, you can upcast this spell to 9th-level by spending 6 hit dice. You can cast this spell this way once per long rest.</p>",
